-- European Stocks Retreat; Old Mutual, Carrefour, Tryg Slide as ITV Advances
-- B y   W i l l   H a d f i e l d
-- 2010-10-15T14:26:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/european-stocks-fluctuate-after-bernanke-speech-peugeot-infineon-advance.html
European stocks retreated, as
declines by Tryg A/S, Old Mutual Plc and Carrefour SA outweighed
gains by ITV Plc and PSA Peugeot Citreon.  The benchmark Stoxx Europe 600 Index dropped 0.5 percent to
264.48 at 3:25 p.m. in London, after earlier gaining as much as
0.4 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
